<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l18"><expan>Dıeth<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Lantſchad<ex>en</ex> <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Aſchaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l19"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vıcʒtum als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / der <expan>gomprechtin<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> geleyt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l20">bey vns ʒu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l21"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals von ʒweyerley Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> gewıllfart vnd oft geleyt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l22">bey vns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd erlengt / daʒ vns doch ʒumal ſwer was / Aber von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l23"><expan>merklıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt vns nıht füklıch der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> gömprechtin Jüdin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l24">geleyt bey vns ʒu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> das in gut von vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l25"><expan>aufcʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l26"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> Jn <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> bartholomeȷ <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="81r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Dieth<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Lantschad<ex>en</ex>,
                                <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>Aschaffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt der
                                <expan>Gomprechtin<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> geleyt bey uns zu
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals von zweyerley juden
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> gewillfart und oft geleyt bey uns
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und erlengt, daz uns doch zumal swer
                        was, aber von <expan>merklich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ist uns niht füklich der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Gömprechtin jüdin geleyt bey uns
                        zu <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> das in gut von uns
                                <expan>aufczuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>, denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Bartholomei
                            <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
